title: Cafe Hanna
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Take-out, Fusion, Middle Eastern, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Greek fusion cafe incorporating dishes and preparation styles from Middle Eastern countries as well as Greece. Menu has a labeled vegan section with a falafel sandwich, eggplant sandwich, and spanikopita. You'll also find a few vegan choices offered in the main menu sections.
